            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2080.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizzas are cooking, combine the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
